item.description:
Hi Girls,

I've got some vacation time coming up during the last week of February and I was thinking of getting away to someplace WARM!! Is anyone interested in trying out the Florida Keys, specifically Key West? I've never been and I'm just beginning the research phase.

I'm emailing to find out if there are any takers for such a trip. Let me know ASAP.

Stay warm and cozy,

Jan
